Started basically from scratch (an older, non raid oriented guild disbanded, like 10 members from it are in sheep) They have done ntov, AoW, Tunare so far, and are probably going to start up ssra soon. With what they know now, the path to emp, vex, elemental planes is laid out for them. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:perpetua;font-size:x-small;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=474148">Arch Mage -- Insidious Blood</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=naladini>naladini</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://img.ranchoweb.com/images/naladini/pills.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 858<br> <font color=#333333>(2/21/03 9:24:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=5>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Can a successful RAID guild be created in today's EQ?</span><hr size=1> It would help if you had a good solid collection of RL friends to get one started. Having a solid core would make things easier.<br>
