Thanks to mudflation, guilds like Sheep are possible now. All velius encounters are now trivial. All of ssra, minus emp perhaps, is trivial.  Just hit the loot pinata for a long enough time, and eventually you'll be passing vex thal. <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:perpetua;font-size:x-small;"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=474148">Arch Mage -- Insidious Blood</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zeem@themagicianstower>Zeem</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 557<br> <font color=#333333>(2/22/03 11:05:56 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Time will tell...</span><hr size=1> I guess it is possible...<br>
